  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/5954ed15bbc185d3a21d4a5dbfda3709.avif?t=1772793903\" width=1228 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One Boss One Fight is an action roguelite built around intense boss battles. You will traverse a dark world, face relentless enemies, and stand against powerful bosses that demand precision and control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple heroes are available, each with their own playstyle. As you progress, you will encounter Viking Gods and earn their benedictions, shaping your build in meaningful ways. Every decision matters. Every mistake is punished.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/559dc6835dcbf2c9a4c74b45780cf145.poster.avif?t=1772793903\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/559dc6835dcbf2c9a4c74b45780cf145.webm?t=1772793903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/559dc6835dcbf2c9a4c74b45780cf145.mp4?t=1772793903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not about clearing rooms of weak enemies. It's about surviving carefully designed encounters where mechanics evolve, patterns shift, and pressure never drops. The world opens through Expeditions, revealing new Bosses, more Challenges, and new combinations of powers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abilities, stars, and constellations enhance your capabilities, allowing deeper builds and long-term progression while keeping each run unpredictable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/6f66358bc031c422c846c4bb71058a54.poster.avif?t=1772793903\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/6f66358bc031c422c846c4bb71058a54.webm?t=1772793903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/6f66358bc031c422c846c4bb71058a54.mp4?t=1772793903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intense Boss Battles</strong> - Multi-phase encounters designed to test positioning, awareness, and execution.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelite Challenge</strong> - Every encounter is unique, with different builds and evolving threats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Progression</strong> - Abilities, stars, and constellations strengthen your heroes and expand your strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Precision Gameplay</strong> - Master timing and movement, or face the consequences.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unforgiving Difficulty</strong> - Only the most skilled players will conquer this World.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/ab1619922f7ed7e3e9aae62a2af8e230.poster.avif?t=1772793903\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/ab1619922f7ed7e3e9aae62a2af8e230.webm?t=1772793903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/ab1619922f7ed7e3e9aae62a2af8e230.mp4?t=1772793903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/7bed0f26e9fc8c4c6a7d0afbb3949cb4.avif?t=1772793903\" width=1228 height=147 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/5954ed15bbc185d3a21d4a5dbfda3709.avif?t=1772793903\" width=1228 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One Boss One Fight is an action roguelite built around intense boss battles. You will traverse a dark world, face relentless enemies, and stand against powerful bosses that demand precision and control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple heroes are available, each with their own playstyle. As you progress, you will encounter Viking Gods and earn their benedictions, shaping your build in meaningful ways. Every decision matters. Every mistake is punished.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/559dc6835dcbf2c9a4c74b45780cf145.poster.avif?t=1772793903\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/559dc6835dcbf2c9a4c74b45780cf145.webm?t=1772793903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/559dc6835dcbf2c9a4c74b45780cf145.mp4?t=1772793903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not about clearing rooms of weak enemies. It's about surviving carefully designed encounters where mechanics evolve, patterns shift, and pressure never drops. The world opens through Expeditions, revealing new Bosses, more Challenges, and new combinations of powers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abilities, stars, and constellations enhance your capabilities, allowing deeper builds and long-term progression while keeping each run unpredictable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/6f66358bc031c422c846c4bb71058a54.poster.avif?t=1772793903\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/6f66358bc031c422c846c4bb71058a54.webm?t=1772793903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/6f66358bc031c422c846c4bb71058a54.mp4?t=1772793903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intense Boss Battles</strong> - Multi-phase encounters designed to test positioning, awareness, and execution.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelite Challenge</strong> - Every encounter is unique, with different builds and evolving threats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Progression</strong> - Abilities, stars, and constellations strengthen your heroes and expand your strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Precision Gameplay</strong> - Master timing and movement, or face the consequences.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unforgiving Difficulty</strong> - Only the most skilled players will conquer this World.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/ab1619922f7ed7e3e9aae62a2af8e230.poster.avif?t=1772793903\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/ab1619922f7ed7e3e9aae62a2af8e230.webm?t=1772793903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/ab1619922f7ed7e3e9aae62a2af8e230.mp4?t=1772793903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908120/extras/7bed0f26e9fc8c4c6a7d0afbb3949cb4.avif?t=1772793903\" width=1228 height=147 /></span></p>",
